Class Database

  • java.lang.Object
    • Database

  • public class Database
extends java.lang.Object
    Database is a class that limits the types it can store to DatabaseTypes. This class will let the user create an index for the database and store data into nodes. An index is a sorted array. This is so the searches can happen quickly.
    Author:
    Jacob Alspaw
